    """
    (import "./baz")

    (let hello baz.hello)
    """
    And a file named "foo/baz.cloe" with:
    """
    (def (hello) (print "Hello, world!"))
    """
    When I successfully run `cloe main.cloe`
    Then the stdout should contain exactly "Hello, world!"

